---
title: Italian Pork Burgers on Garlic-Buttered Buns with Oven Fries
description: Not to get cheesy, but we’re head over heels for these bodacious burgers. Juicy, Italian-spiced pork patties are topped with melty mozz and a tangle of tangy-sweet balsamic caramelized onions. Everything is then tucked into toasty garlic butter buns (read: garlic bread!) and served with a heap of crispy potato wedges. Pig out!
